# UI/UX- und Frontend-Regeln (essence-intern)

## Layout-Grundregeln

- 12-Spalten-Layout mit:
  - Horizontaler Gutter: 24px
  - Vertikaler Abstand: 16px
- Breakpoints: mobile-first (`sm`, `md`, `lg`, `xl`)

```tsx
// Beispiel: Layout-Grid
<div className="grid grid-cols-12 gap-x-6 gap-y-4">
  <div className="col-span-12 md:col-span-6">Inhalt</div>
  <div className="col-span-12 md:col-span-6">Inhalt</div>
</div>
````

